   <text>
      <body divRole="original-translation">
         <div type="original" xml:lang="nl">
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.1" f="1r" facs="#s1r" n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Beste J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Hoe zeer ’t mij spijt, ik kan geen afspraak maken, ik ben <hi rend="italics">te</hi> onzeker van mijn tijd. Tenminste de eerste dagen, misschien op ’t eind der week zal ik je even schrijven.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.3" n="3" rend="indent">Je bent toch vrij zooals gezegd.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.orig.nl.4" n="4">Salut.</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.orig.nl.2" f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.1"
                corresp="#pb.orig.nl.1"
                f="1r"
                facs="#s1r"
                n="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.1" corresp="#p.orig.nl.1" n="1">Dear J.,</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.2" corresp="#p.orig.nl.2" n="2">Much as it disappoints me I can’t make an appointment, I’m not sure about my time. At least for the next few days, perhaps at the end of the week, I’ll drop you a line.</p>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.3" corresp="#p.orig.nl.3" n="3" rend="indent">You’re free after all, as you’ve said. </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p xml:id="p.tr.en.4" corresp="#p.orig.nl.4" n="4">Salut.</p>
            <pb xml:id="pb.tr.en.2" corresp="#pb.orig.nl.2" f="1v" facs="#s1v" n="2"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
